子站悼念呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545797</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b07f6013bf64800634022c55d3b83c379f16ec9e","tid":1545692,"uid":34780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:11:48.000Z","msg":"----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n太子CCTV最快星期6會被刪除<br />\n我地要有一次大集氣出太子 制造輿論壓力<br />\n將831死人嘅概念植入市民心中<br />\n令全港市民聚焦落黨鐵 迫佢交831嘅CCTV<br />\n絕對唔係要依兩日咁得幾十人圍太子警署咁<br />\n一定要上千人<br />\n實行將太子站鋪滿白色鮮花<br />\n<br />\n若然屬實 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日就係手足頭七</span></span><br />\n依家號召各位巴打<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日9月6號1930集氣萬人太子站獻花<br />\n將《願榮光歸香港》獻俾手足</span></span><br />\n見字嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">巴打幫手spread出去</span></span> 一個人真係推唔起<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0eLgNaX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0eLgNaX.jpg&h=ec9aaa6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n【831】9月6號1930集氣千人太子站獻花行動post<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544326\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544326</a><br />\n<br />\n今晚8:31PM將國歌獻給太子死難者<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545416</a>"},{"pid":"d2af48637f034bede41b1360bf8db52b8e76e4ed","tid":1545692,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:15:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"68032912eca3a44d028b928c1b51248a79af756f","tid":1545692,"uid":186602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25a7f2de68482056e4fbf0c03f2f3fedd71c01f0","tid":1545692,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:19:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}